    "Description": "Beat It – Epic Metal Orchestra Version That Will Shock You\n\nWelcome to the ultimate Epic Symphonic Metal Orchestra experience.\nThis playlist delivers powerful orchestral arrangements blended with heavy metal energy, cinematic soundscapes, and epic symphonic intensity.\n\nFrom dark symphonic metal to heroic battle themes, every track is crafted to bring you a Hollywood-style metal atmosphere — perfect for workouts, gaming, studying, driving, or simply diving into powerful cinematic sound.\n\nIf you love bands like Nightwish, Within Temptation, Epica, or cinematic composers like Hans Zimmer and Two Steps From Hell, this collection is made for you.\n\n⚔️ Epic orchestration\n🔥 Powerful metal energy\n🎻 Cinematic symphonic arrangements\n🎧 Immersive sound experience\n\nSubscribe and turn on notifications to never miss new epic releases from Tetraz Metal Orchestra — where metal meets the symphony.\n\n\n#EpicMetal #SymphonicMetal #MetalOrchestra #OrchestralMetal #CinematicMetal #EpicMusic #MetalPlaylist #SymphonicRock #PowerfulMusic #EpicOrchestra #BattleMusic #DarkMetal #MetalAnthems #CinematicOrchestra #TetrazMetalOrchestra",
